c: 2
v: 171
t: "Ekifaananyi ky'abantu abo abatakkiriza n'oyo abakoowoola okujja eri obukkiriza kiringa omulunzi akoowoola ensoloze ne zijja gy'ali naye nga tezitegeera ky'aziyitira wabula okuwulira amaloboozi n'okukoowoolwa. (Abatakkiriza abo) Bakiggala, bakassiru, bamuzibe, tebagenda kutegeera kintu kyonna"